{1: '1', 2: 'Liv', 3: 'Commandant, according to the record analysis of the system monitor station, a data fluctuation with a deviation value of 0.0274 was captured not long after the mission was released. But since it was fixed soon...', 4: '1'}

{1: '1', 2: 'Lucia', 3: 'The analysis of the memory coordinate information has been uploaded to the tactical terminal.', 4: '1'}

{1: '1', 2: 'Lucia', 3: 'I see. Thanks for your help.', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lee', 3: 'Lucia is quite good at communicating with such kind of person...', 4: '1'}
